{"tid":1236204,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"血債票償，快d check, 唔好比人用陰招取消左選民！","createTime":"2019-06-17T11:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:02:59.000Z","uid":261331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a91314ee3accbf5e412370b229f34fcc77147ce9","tid":1236204,"uid":261331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:18:37.000Z","msg":"[廣傳]有人無信通知下取消左選民！記得check 完快d 登記返做選民呀，急！登記好簡單，唔會阻你好多時間！<br />\n<br />\n***自己回家申請唔好向街填***<br />\n<br />\nCheck link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCnKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=e36347aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不幸重新要申請（REO-1 表格)，下載後填完重新上載，無須地址證明：<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Findex.jsp&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCnKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=2c915e26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp</a> //<br />\n&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;<a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Findex.jsp&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCnKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=2c915e26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp</a> //<br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"eeab70300ae01a8467d27df456999daa810d6584","tid":1236204,"uid":206812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVtCeWR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVtCeWR.png&h=06622b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190618&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59729373\" data-sr-ur